title: Monumento a la Revolucion
author: jugarbien & Narj0s
pages:
This is a work in
progress Monumento a
la revolucion, or the
Monument to the
revolution!
This is a giant relic of
what would've been a
massive palace built
by a dictator in the
early 1900s, with this
as it's entrance, so
you can imagine how
big it would've been.
Said dictator was
overthrown and killed
before construction
was ever finished, and
this was left as a
monument to the
revolution
